snippet.title: Sultan Of Egypt
snippet.description: Features of this game is an atmospheric story game with choices. There are Puzzle, mini war, and a very nice interactive story in the game. True beauty is always beyond imagination; and a story, or anything for that matter, is important, only to the extent it reflects a ray of it.
